作**：从1573ms → 11164ms（7.1倍延迟）\n- 这是整个调用链中最下游的异常，直接影响cartservice\n\n### 2. **错误传播路径**\n```\nRedis (根因) → cartservice (受害者) → frontend (受害者)\n```\n\n### 3. **影响范围**\n- **cartservice**：由于Redis性能问题，cartservice的响应时间显著增加\n- **frontend**：出现大量404错误，表明服务无法正常响应\n- **其他服务**：productcatalogservice和currencyservice也出现轻微延迟\n\n### 4. **建议排查方向**\n- Redis集群状态和资源使用情况\n- 网络连接和带宽问题\n- Redis内存使用和GC情况\n- 数据库连接池配置\n\n**结论**：系统故障的主要根因是Redis性能严重下降，导致cartservice响应延迟，最终引发frontend服务不可用。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Log Findings for Full Context", "consensus_decision": "AGREED", "current_hypothesis": "redis-cart-0 is the root cause due to severe performance degradation (HGET/HMSET operations latency increased 5-7 times)"}
